{"tid":759543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[口交=？？] 外交部：美駐華大使館爆炸是個別事件","createTime":"2018-07-28T16:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T20:25:42.000Z","uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"49774ac91951b9b2995a18c9896edd533866f257","tid":759543,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T16:51:10.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國駐華大使館外發生爆炸，外圍一度封鎖一個多小時，北京公安公布，是一名男子燃點爆竹裝置引起爆燃導致手部受傷，事件沒有其他傷者。<br />\n<br />\n外交部回應美國駐華大使館外的爆炸，認為是個別事件。<br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人耿爽：「這起發生在朝陽區天澤路和安家樓路十字路口的事件，是一起孤立的治安事件，中國的警方已經即時妥善地進行處理。」"},{"pid":"8e8ecea24fa2f794157ee239d596b4b147ff96a0","tid":759543,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T16:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全部都是我的人"},{"pid":"32b3ffe4b28e392fd929596e4a9abfbd114e5d0b","tid":759543,"uid":169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T17:52:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfa54ac9c4f0894d7ce2dac39bebbaeacf59775f","tid":759543,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T18:09:17.000Z","msg":"刁種會唔會搵人行刺侵侵？"},{"pid":"0975337ced40e8f7c84da2dc699b0e7a771066cc","tid":759543,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T20:25:42.000Z","msg":"小事都要口交部出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}